@page "/"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<h1>Hydration Reminder & Weather Display</h1>

<p>
    Welcome to my first Blazor project! This app demonstrates how to build a frontend-only Blazor Web App
    without relying on databases or APIs. It combines two simple but practical features:
</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Hydration Tracker:</strong> A counter that helps you track daily water intake.</li>
    <li><strong>Weather Forecasts:</strong> A playful weather table with comfort index, emojis, and lifestyle tips.</li>
</ul>

<p>
    <b>Tech Stack:</b> Blazor Web App (.NET 8), Bootstrap styling, frontend-only logic.
</p>